# NGS Data Analysis Pipeline

> Modular, reproducible NGS pipeline for genomics research | HPC-ready

## Overview

A modular next-generation sequencing (NGS) data analysis pipeline covering
the complete workflow from raw FASTQ reads to annotated variants and
differential expression results. Designed for reproducible execution on
HPC clusters and Galaxy platform.

