## Tools used

| Step | Tool | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| QC | FastQC, MultiQC | Per-base quality, adapter content, GC bias |
| Trim | Trimmomatic, Fastp | Adapter removal, quality trimming |
| Align (DNA) | BWA-MEM, Bowtie2 | Reference genome alignment |
| Align (RNA) | HISAT2, STAR | Splice-aware alignment |
| SAM/BAM | SAMtools, Picard | Format conversion, sort, index, dedup |
| Variant calling | GATK HaplotypeCaller | SNPs and INDELs |
| Counting | featureCounts | Read quantification per gene |
| DE analysis | DESeq2, edgeR (R) | Differential expression |
| Annotation | SnpEff, VEP | Functional variant annotation |
| Visualisation | IGV, UCSC Browser | Genome browser inspection |

