## File formats

| Format | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| FASTQ | Raw reads вЂ” 4 lines per read |
| SAM/BAM | Aligned reads вЂ” BAM is binary/compressed |
| VCF | Variant calls вЂ” CHROM POS REF ALT QUAL |
| GTF/GFF | Gene annotation |
| BED | Genomic intervals (0-based) |

